    • addBoneExtraData

      ModelEntity addBoneExtraData(String boneName, ExtraBoneData data)
      Dynamic modification of bone.

      Direct modification will result in the loss of existing additional data for the bone. Please use getBoneExtraData(java.lang.String) to get the existing data before modifying it.

      参数:
      boneName - Bone name
      data - data
      返回:
      ModelEntity

      ModelEntity inactive(String model)
      The client will only render a fixed model of the body at the current position.

      Please set to cancel entity AI before setting, otherwise it will cause activities such as attacks on other entities by the entity that are not visible to the client.

      返回:
      ModelEntity
